text: Kagiya Shiksa-an o Allah so manga Monapik a manga Mama go so manga Monapik a manga Babai, go so manga Pananakoto a manga Mama go so manga Pananakoto a manga Babai, go Phakataobatun o Allah so Miyamaratiyaya a manga Mama, go so Miyamaratiyaya a manga Babai: Na Tatap a so Allah na Manapi, a Makalimo-on
